Interface ISecOcCryptoServiceMapping

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICryptoServiceMapping, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface ISecOcCryptoServiceMapping
extends IEntity, ICryptoServiceMapping
    ISecOcCryptoServiceMapping: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class has the ability to represent a crypto service mapping for the Pdu-based communication via SecOC.
